sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Пользователь
    participant UI as Экран апноэ
    participant Rec as MediaRecorder / AVAudioSession
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Svc as services/apnea.py
    participant M as apnea_model.predict
    participant IDB as IndexedDB

    U->>UI: запускает запись
    UI->>Rec: start()
    Rec-->>UI: аудиофайл (wav/mp3)
    UI->>API: POST /apnea/analyze (multipart)
    API->>Svc: run_apnea(path)
    Svc->>M: predict(audio_path)
    M-->>Svc: (has_apnea, confidence)
    Svc-->>API: (has_apnea, confidence, used_model)
    API-->>UI: {has_apnea, confidence, mode}
    UI->>IDB: put(apnea_results)
    UI-->>U: результат + история
